1 install sudo, build-essential, python3, python3-venv, python3-pip, git,libopencv-dev, libeigen3-dev, ninja-build, libboost-all-dev, libssl-dev
2 build pangolin from source (https://github.com/stevenlovegrove/Pangolin.git) 
2.1 run this script to install the prerequisites ./scripts/install_prerequisites.sh recommended
2.2 cmake -B build -GNinja
2.3 cmake --build build
2.4 cmake --build build -t install

3.0 git clone https://github.com/devansh0703/ORB_SLAM3.git
3.2 run the build script
